    "en": {
      "title": "Oil prices rise",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ceylon Petroleum Corporation and the Ceylon Indian Oil Company have taken steps to increase fuel prices. The fuel price has been increased with effect from 2.00 am today.",
        "Accordingly, a 92 liter octane petrol has been increased by Rs. 50 and the new price is Rs. 470.",
        "A liter of 95 octane petrol has been increased by Rs. 100 and the new price is Rs. 550.",
        "A liter of auto diesel has been increased by Rs. 60 and the new price is Rs. 460.",
        "A liter of Super Diesel has been increased by Rs. 75 and the new price is Rs. 520."
      ],
